neighborhood_overview: Welcome to Tetuán, the vibrant heart of Madrid! This multicultural neighborhood offers a unique experience where tradition blends with modernity. Explore its bustling streets filled with shops, restaurants, and tapas bars, where you can taste authentic Spanish cuisine. Immerse yourself in its rich history by visiting iconic landmarks such as Plaza de Castilla and Parque Rodríguez Sahagún, perfect for relaxing and enjoying nature. With excellent public transportation connections, you'll be just minutes away from the city center and all its major attractions.
